  "title": "Operations Admin Coordinator (Junior/Senior)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide administrative support to daily operations work</li>\n  <li>Administer Order Processing duties, including data entry and updating of records to system</li>\n  <li>Assist in the planning and scheduling of measurement and installation works based on existing procedures and customer requirements</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with relevant Departments in daily deployment of trucks and drivers</li>\n  <li>Assist in Vehicle Scheduling</li>\n  <li>Prepare drawings with/without using CAD software</li>\n  <li>Coordinate between different departments and sub-contractors to ensure order fulfilment and proper documentation and billing</li>\n  <li>Prepare full of documents including costing before passing over to other departments for processing</li>\n  <li>Perform verification of sub-contractor billings</li>\n  <li>Handle office administrative work like filing and scanning</li>\n  <li>All other job duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess at least a secondary school GCE “O” level or Diploma equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 1 – 2 year(s) of working experience in admin co-ordination</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently under minimum supervision</li>\n  <li>Able to work in a fast-paced environment with deadlines</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office (Excel, Outlook) and Google Sheets</li>\n  <li>Comfortable with Numbers and Technical Drawings</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with Singapore roads will be an advantage</li>\n</ul>",
